Simulating with Delayed Differential Equations
    - Python based approach
        - https://arxiv.org/abs/0911.1633
        - http://pydelay.sourceforge.net/       
        Download pydelay-0.1.1.tar.gz
        Extract and within folder
            $ sudo python3 setup.py install
                # Fix errors due to python3
                    raise sintax in _dde23.py
                # Other errors in doc related files
                    Ignored
        Requires Weaver, which is deprecated
        
        Delete installation
            python setup.py install --record files.txt to generate the list
            cat files.txt | sudo xargs rm -rf
            sudo rm -rf /usr/local/lib/python3.5/dist-packages/pydelay

    -MATLAB based approach
        https://www.mathworks.com/help/matlab/ref/dde23.html
        http://www.runet.edu/~thompson/webddes/tutorial.pdf
        http://www.mathworks.com/matlabcentral/fileexchange/3899-tutorial-on-solving-ddes-with-dde23
